      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-28/china-stock-euphoria-takes-hold-as-traders-overlook-deeper-woes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国股市多头之前已经多次遭受损失，但当前的狂热浪潮如此强劲，让他们把谨慎抛到了九霄云外。]]></description>
